headline: Morgan Stanley Shows Huge, Unusual Call Options Volume - Are Investors Bullish?
summary: Morgan Stanley is showing huge amounts of volume in call options that expire on Friday. It could be a signal that investors are bullish on MS stock. The investment banking firm had strong Q2 earnings, implying potential upside.

headline: One Big Beautiful Bill Act a tailwind for Apple and others - Morgan Stanley
summary: Investing.com -- Morgan Stanley stated in a note on Wednesday that it anticipates the One Big Beautiful Bill Act (OBBBA) will provide a meaningful boost to free cash flow (FCF) across the IT hardware sector, with Apple (NASDAQ:AAPL) among the primary beneficiaries.
